<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer.BindResourceArray" Title="BindResourceArray method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer">IStateContainer</PageRef> ->
    BindResourceArray
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>BindResourceArray</TypeRef> method sets up a binding to either an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArray">IDataArray</PageRef>
      or <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITexelArray">ITexelArray</PageRef> object.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        In order to create or bind to a resource array, the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.Feature">ResourceArrays feature</PageRef>
        must be supported on the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice">IGraphicsDevice</PageRef>, and
        activated when the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.CreateRenderer">CreateRenderer</PageRef>
        method is called.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void BindResourceArray(ResourceArrayId resourceArrayId, IDataArray* resourceBuffer, bool resetCounter = true);
void BindResourceArray(ResourceArrayId resourceArrayId, ITexelArray* resourceBuffer);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="ResourceArrayId!cobalt.graphics.ResourceArrayId" Name="resourceArrayId">
          The <TypeRef>ResourceArrayId</TypeRef> of the resource array to bind
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IDataArray*!cobalt.graphics.IDataArray" Name="resourceBuffer">
          The <TypeRef>IDataArray</TypeRef> to bind
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="ITexelArray*!cobalt.graphics.ITexelArray" Name="resourceBuffer">
          The <TypeRef>ITexelArray</TypeRef> to bind
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="bool" Name="resetCounter">
          When binding an <TypeRef>IDataArray</TypeRef> with an attached counter, specifies whether the counter should
          be reset when this binding is performed.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
